OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FNorthern Scotland is expected to face
OL,7,Fmore heavy snow on Tuesday, after a
OL,8,Fday when hundreds of schools in the
OL,9,Fregion were shut and travel was widely
OL,10,Fdisrupted.
OL,12,FAn amber warning for snow has been
OL,13,Fissued for large parts of northeast
OL,14,Fand northern Scotland from 11am until
OL,15,F7pm on Tuesday, with forecasters
OL,16,Fwarning of 5-10cm of snow widely, and
OL,17,Fup to 15cm in places.
