OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FThe areas covered by the warning
OL,7,Finclude parts of Aberdeen,
OL,8,FAberdeenshire, Moray, Highland, Angus
OL,9,Fand Perth and Kinross.
OL,11,FA yellow warning of snow and ice is in
OL,12,Fplace as far south as Perth until
OL,13,Fmidnight on Tuesday.
OL,15,FThe Met Office has also issued a
OL,16,Fyellow warning of snow and ice from
OL,17,Fthe central belt south down beyond the
OL,18,Fborder, until 11am on Tuesday.
