OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FPupils enjoyed an unexpected extra day
OL,7,Fof holiday at schools in Shetland,
OL,8,FOrkney, the Western Isles and
OL,9,FAberdeenshire, and dozens in Moray
OL,10,Fwere also shut.
OL,12,FIn Aberdeen city, dozens of schools
OL,13,Fwere closed for the day after opening
OL,14,Fwas initially delayed until 11am.
OL,16,FThe weather also disrupted rail
OL,17,Ftravel, and the Inverness to Wick/
OL,18,FThurso, Inverness to Kyle, Inverness
OL,19,Fto Aberdeen and Aberdeen to Dundee
OL,20,Flines were shut after heavy snow
OL,21,Fdrifted on to the tracks.
