OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FDespite multiple snowploughs and
OL,7,Fspecialist teams being deployed across
OL,8,Fthe affected lines, on Monday ScotRail
OL,9,Fsaid most will remain shut on Tuesday
OL,10,Fwhile further work is carried out.
OL,12,FGary Hopkirk, route programme director
OL,13,Fat Network Rail Scotland, said: "Deep
OL,14,Fsnow can pose a serious risk to the
OL,15,Frailway, and when snow depth exceeds
OL,16,F30cm, trains can't run safely unless
OL,17,Ffitted with snow ploughs.
