OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,F"Our teams are working as hard as they
OL,7,Fcan, however, in some parts the
OL,8,Fsnowdrifts are forming as quickly as
OL,9,Fwe're clearing them.
OL,11,F"We'll only reopen lines and return to
OL,12,Fnormal operations once we're confident
OL,13,Fit's safe to do so. We appreciate the
OL,14,Fpatience of passengers while we manage
OL,15,Fthe impact of this heavy snowfall."
OL,17,FMark Ilderton, from ScotRail, said the
OL,18,Fmajority of the ScotRail network
OL,19,Fremains open despite the "challenging"
OL,20,Fweather conditions.
