OL,6,FHe said: "The Met Office yellow
OL,7,Fweather warning for snow and ice has
OL,8,Fbeen extended until Tuesday, 6
OL,9,FJanuary, covering the entire country.
OL,11,F"Conditions can change quickly, so
OL,12,Fwe'd encourage customers to plan ahead
OL,13,Fand check their journey before
OL,14,Ftravelling."
OL,16,FSome flights have also been disrupted.
