OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FLoganair cancelled flights from
OL,7,FAberdeen and Inverness airports, and a
OL,8,Fnumber of flights to and from Sumburgh
OL,9,FAirport in Shetland were cancelled, as
OL,10,Fwere several departures from Kirkwall
OL,11,FAirport in Orkney.
OL,13,FA Highlands and Islands Airports
OL,14,FLimited (HIAL) spokesman said:
OL,15,F"Forecasted adverse weather may impact
OL,16,Fflight schedules across Scotland.
OL,17,FPlease contact your airline for the
OL,18,Flatest flight information before
OL,19,Ftravelling."
