OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FOn the roads motorists faced difficult
OL,7,Fdriving conditions.
OL,9,FThe A90 was closed between Goval and
OL,10,FCraibstone at Bogenjoss, and snow
OL,11,Fgates were closed on the A939 between
OL,12,FCock Bridge and Tomintoul and the B974
OL,13,FBridge of Dye.
OL,15,FInfrastructure firm Amey said all 27
OL,16,Ftrunk routes in the south west of the
OL,17,Fcountry will receive "double salt
OL,18,Ftreatments" at 1pm and 1am throughout
OL,19,Fmost of the week, and all 15 patrol
OL,20,Fgritters will remain on the network
OL,21,Fcontinuously.
