OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FFrom the central belt south
OL,7,Fforecasters predict an area of "mainly
OL,8,Flight snow" with most places likely to
OL,9,Fhave no more than 1-2cm.
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Alan
OL,12,FWaddell, of Police Scotland, said:
OL,13,F"The forecasted heavy snow showers and
OL,14,Fice means driving conditions are
OL,15,Flikely to be hazardous in some areas.
OL,17,F"Our advice is to plan ahead and
OL,18,Fconsider if your journey is really
OL,19,Fnecessary during the weather warnings."
