OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FMinisters met police, local
OL,7,Fauthorities, utilities companies and
OL,8,Fother bodies on Monday to discuss
OL,9,Frecovery efforts and to prepare for
OL,10,Ffurther snow and ice warnings.
OL,12,FAfter the meeting, First Minister John
OL,13,FSwinney said snow across northern
OL,14,FScotland has had a "significant"
OL,15,Fimpact, and that a "huge effort" was
OL,16,Fgoing into keeping transport moving
OL,17,Fand public services open.
