OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,F"At present, there is still some
OL,7,Ftravel disruption but trunk roads are
OL,8,Fopen and rail, ferry and air services
OL,9,Fare working to get back to normal as
OL,10,Fquickly as possible," he said.
OL,12,F"Likewise, many schools are closed
OL,13,Ftoday but remote learning is in place
OL,14,Ffor young people while contingency
OL,15,Fplans are in place for affected health
OL,16,Fand social care services.
