OL,3,CForecasters warn of more heavy snow
OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,F"There will be further snow and ice,
OL,7,Fwith yellow warnings in large parts of
OL,8,FScotland and temperatures set to
OL,9,Fremain cold, so impacts will continue
OL,10,Fto be felt in the coming days which
OL,11,Fcould include transport problems and I
OL,12,Fwould encourage everyone to plan
OL,13,Fahead, look out for each other and pay
OL,14,Fclose attention to the range of
OL,15,Fweather and travel advice available."
