OL,4,Cacross swathes of northern Scotland
OL,6,FMr Swinney also paid tribute to the
OL,7,F"truly exceptional" efforts of
OL,8,Ffarmers, volunteers and members of the
OL,9,Fpublic in helping clear roads, dig out
OL,10,Fcars and keep people safe, which he
OL,11,Fsaid showed "heartening" community
OL,12,Fspirit.
OL,14,FHe added that ministers will continue
OL,15,Fto keep the situation "under review".
